Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.02,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord3\c&HC2B9E8&\3c&HB26147&\fs80\fad(300,0)}戀愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.02,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord3\c&HC2B9E8&\3c&HB26147&\fs80\fad(300,0)}心理測試
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這本書輝夜已經閱讀完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:13.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,提問 你撿了一隻松鼠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.57,0:11:15.91,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,她能夠迴避危險的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你會怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:19.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我會每天都給它做好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:21.69,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,睡前給它做按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.23,0:11:23.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,答案就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:27.02,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,結婚後會怎麼對待伴侶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,換而言之
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個名為「心理測試」的地雷區裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:35.23,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她有著莫大的優勢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我覺得是藤原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.43,0:11:40.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 是我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,陰暗的路…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:59.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要逃跑呢 石上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:02.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我看見的是四宮前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:03.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上同學是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很聽話 也不惹人討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.88,0:12:13.90,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我一直隻把你當作蟲子看待
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:19.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,問題是會長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜最怕又黑又可怕的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.91,0:12:28.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 我們一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.40,0:12:34.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼藤原書記在偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:34.24,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,偷笑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:39.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙剛才說過這是有趣的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:42.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,能吸引那個戀愛腦的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:44.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不會是正常的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:46.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果這個結果是喜歡的人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.35,0:12:52.99,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒呦 會長 你潛意識裡那麼喜歡我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:56.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就像告白一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.61,0:13:03.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,最好是回答會令他們滿意的與他們無關的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:04.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:07.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我的妹妹…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.69,0:13:14.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拍你肩膀的是你喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.94,0:13:17.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說會長你是個妹控啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:19.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你的回答最無聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對 我是妹控
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:26.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡四宮前輩？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這更像恐怖的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:39.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長 我好像得了斯德哥爾摩綜合症
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:40.20,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:43.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 保重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:46.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可能還有吊橋效應並發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去醫院檢查一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:52.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想回答 在網上搜索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:56.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,完了 藤原同學在書以外的地方找題了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 這題好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.26,0:14:02.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你現在在一片花田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.04,0:14:07.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,花田的主人說你想拿多少就拿多少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.50,0:14:09.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你會拿走多少呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.66,0:14:12.14,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,看不出測試結果的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:13.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.19,0:14:20.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我會認真選出很少的幾朵非常好看的花帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:26.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我會摘做一捧喜歡的花束的量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.50,0:14:28.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:31.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 順口說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.05,0:14:34.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長會拿多少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:38.31,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,反正不是剛才那種對人有指向性的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:39.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,遵循本心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.59,0:14:42.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,免費並且想拿多少就拿多少對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:44.37,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼答案只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.69,0:14:51.20,Kaguya_zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&HCFA061&\3c&H6E412D&\fs60\bord5}堆滿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:47.57,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拿走整整一卡車的量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我覺得一卡車都還少
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:53.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,鐵公雞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:56.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拿那麼多走能幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.93,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,送人或者賣掉都可以嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.34,0:15:00.05,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,測試結果是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:00.58,Kaguya_hm_heiti,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H3E2623&\b1\bord3\3c&HD1D94F&}點擊查看測試結果
