Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,回家要不要順便去吃思慕雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.53,0:15:42.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:44.29,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要西芹的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:45.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要什麼的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:52.64,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 我今天要去打工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 又去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.32,0:15:55.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,工作狂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.16,0:15:57.78,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一定要去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.13,0:15:59.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:05.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,該回去了 輝夜大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.07,0:16:10.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早坂 我不是說過不要來學生會室了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.73,0:16:14.11,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我確認過會長還有其他人都已經回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.29,0:16:15.41,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:16.49,Kaguya_hm_title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(500,400)\bord4\fs80\pos(1330,896)}輝夜大小姐想被注意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.89,0:16:18.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,放鬆警惕是最致命的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你最近變散漫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這幅打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:25.84,Kaguya_hm_miaowu,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H093460&\fs90\move(472,864,472,0,0,3419)}敞\N開\N衣\N領
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.13,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還有指甲
