Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.56,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,裙子的長短都違反校規了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:30.72,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,都在校規允許的範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:34.05,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有一點鑽校規的空子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:35.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.11,0:16:38.66,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,對於我們來說美貌就是力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.96,0:16:45.18,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,在社交界不粉飾自己的人沒有立足之地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:48.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不想被只有臉好看的女人搶走機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.97,0:16:51.39,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說輝夜大小姐太死板了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:55.63,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我們學校流行輕美甲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:58.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想讓男生覺得可愛的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.30,0:17:00.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還是要稍微充實自己比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:01.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:03.00,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話會長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.36,0:17:06.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不對 男生會覺得可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:09.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真虧你這種破綻百出的說話方式還能堅持到現在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.15,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:16.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早坂知道到美甲不會吸引異性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:17.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:18.35,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,男生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.82,0:17:21.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 趕快回去塗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.73,0:17:27.21,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是想讓輝夜打扮的心情作祟讓她含糊其辭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:24.58,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.45,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係的 很快就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:27.50,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 等下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.47,0:17:33.87,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不觸犯服裝規定的半透明美甲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.39,0:17:38.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只在無名指上點的鑽彰顯了謙虛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:44.43,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長會怎麼想 會覺得可愛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:48.70,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還是會覺得不夠正經
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:53.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,把指甲弄成那樣是要怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:18:00.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不想這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:04.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,果然今天還是先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.97,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼呢 四宮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:08.40,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不進去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:11.32,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我現在就進去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:15.74,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,輝夜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.68,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這部分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:25.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你後面藏了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.04,0:18:27.83,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.03,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,只有這種事敏銳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:34.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就算要被發現我也希望是會長發現
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:36.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不是她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:38.81,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要再近一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.10,0:18:43.55,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長這是之前的會議記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:45.36,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,有勞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:52.52,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這裡的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:57.24,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:18:59.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.34,0:19:04.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有發現
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮打扮起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:11.06,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼 難道是說對我沒興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.34,0:19:12.86,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼心境變化了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:15.08,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都說「天鵝會打扮嗎」這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有打扮的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.97,0:19:20.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 這是雷區嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.61,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你長得很安產
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.73,0:19:26.10,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這算不算性騷擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:27.71,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,小圭 你這個裙子太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.41,0:19:32.98,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是穿給哥哥你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你這是性騷擾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.12,0:19:35.89,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.39,0:19:38.53,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是作為哥哥關心一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.66,0:19:41.67,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,除了她想讓看到的那個人以外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.71,0:19:44.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,其他人的反應都有被定義為性騷擾的傾向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.27,0:19:47.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 既然注意到了還是說一下比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.87,0:19:51.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也不會比我妹說的更過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:55.45,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,藤原前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你換護髮素了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.75,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 你知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:06.19,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 和平時的味道不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.21,0:20:11.65,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有種比較濃的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:14.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但比平時味道得更可愛一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:17.49,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,要形容的話 就像嬰兒身上的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:22.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,石上同學 好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.80,0:20:25.22,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.34,0:20:32.04,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去死 先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:34.44,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 但是別死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:40.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很好聞的味道 本來是想誇她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:44.25,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我身上有味兒嗎 很臭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:45.79,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.82,0:20:47.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果哪天四宮也說我噁心的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:48.95,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我也可能想死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:51.96,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是不要說美甲的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:53.85,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣風險太高了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:56.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕對不要被說噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:00.62,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不 這也是藉口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.00,0:21:04.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.51,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不稱讚四宮的指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.65,0:21:13.12,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,純粹是因為我在害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:25.47,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,結果他還是沒注意美甲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:29.59,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他沒注意到更好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.37,0:21:34.77,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,果然我這種人即使打扮了也沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:40.34,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒辦法變可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.95,0:21:42.58,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,四宮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.73,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那個指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:57.82,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.14,0:22:03.76,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？你說完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:05.33,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,會長真可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:06.80,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還會害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:12.28,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.60,0:22:14.16,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然輝夜大小姐也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:18.30,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他想說什麼呢 早坂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:21.38,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,早 坂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.16,0:22:24.13,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,他說我指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.57,0:22:27.52,Kaguya_an8,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 早 坂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.82,0:22:26.46,Kaguya_zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今日戰局 輝夜勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:42.80,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　きっと今同じ気持ちだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.62,0:22:42.80,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 現在一定懷著同樣的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:59.90,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君から笑いかけてくれたなら　天使でいられるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:59.90,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}只要有你的微笑 我就還能如天使一般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:05.90,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}気付いたの　試されてる　意地悪な駆け引きで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:05.90,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已經注意到我在用壞心眼的謀略考驗他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.95,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}後にはもう引けないから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.95,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}已經不能退縮了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:11.78,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}仕掛けてあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:11.78,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}讓我給你設下圈套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:18.96,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}さあ　掛かってみせて　戸惑ってみせて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.87,0:23:18.96,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}來吧 掉進陷阱吧 不知所措吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:29.05,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}そして最後に伝えてみせて　好きだって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:29.05,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}然後在最後說出那句喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:36.72,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}君と私　どんな風に恋するの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.13,0:23:36.72,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}你和我 將會怎樣相戀呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:40.60,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}探る RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:40.60,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}去探索 RELATION
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:48.24,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}余裕なんてないよ　見つめられる度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:48.24,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}每次被你注視 我一點都不從容哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:52.03,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}いつも震えてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.36,0:23:52.03,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}我總是會顫抖著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:59.04,Kaguya_ed_JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}素直じゃない私を連れ出して！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:59.04,Kaguya_ed_ZH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur5}請帶走這樣不坦率的我！
